#Eventstore Docker image

This Dockerfile builds an image for the latest stable release of [Eventstore](https://www.geteventstore.com/downloads/), with Mono statically linked. 

*Build* using `build.sh`. It will produce the image `eventstore:latest`.

*Run* using `run.sh`. The `2113` and `1113` ports must be specified. The `/data/db` and `/data/logs` volumes must be specified. Put all of the parameters you need for the Eventstore service into the run command (e.g. `--ext-http-prefixes=http://*:2113/ --ext-ip=0.0.0.0`).
